  30:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c **** 
  31:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****        (+) Possibility to disable or enable Analog Noise Filter
  32:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****        (+) Use of a configured Digital Noise Filter
  33:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****        (+) Disable or enable wakeup from Stop mode(s)
