  35:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c **** 
  36:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****                      ##### How to use this driver #####
  37:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
  38:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   [..] This driver provides functions to configure Noise Filter and Wake Up Feature
  39:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****     (#) Configure I2C Analog noise filter using the function HAL_I2CEx_ConfigAnalogFilter()
  40:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****     (#) Configure I2C Digital noise filter using the function HAL_I2CEx_ConfigDigitalFilter()
  41:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****     (#) Configure the enable or disable of I2C Wake Up Mode using the functions :
  42:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****           (++) HAL_I2CEx_EnableWakeUp()
  43:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****           (++) HAL_I2CEx_DisableWakeUp()
  44:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****     (#) Configure the enable or disable of fast mode plus driving capability using the functions :
  45:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****           (++) HAL_I2CEx_ConfigFastModePlus()
  46:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_i2c_ex.c ****   @endverbatim
